[[File:Con_Plasma_Satallite.png|right|thumb|A Plasma Burst Satellite]]
'''Plasma Burst Satellites''' were similar to laser defense satellites. They were loaded with powerful [[Plasma/Legends|plasma]] blasts, shot from two turrets stationed on top of the satellite. One round was enough to destroy even the strongest fighter craft. Multiple shots could take down the [[Deflector shield/Legends|shields]] of [[Corvette/Legends|corvettes]] and [[Frigate/Legends|frigates]]. It was not nearly as effective against multiple [[Squadron/Legends|squadrons]] of [[Starfighter/Legends|fighters]] and frigates.

